 A warrant of arrest was issued against Onyekanna and Ezenwa, known by aliases ‘50 cent’ and ‘Alex’ respectively in August 2016, after Hawks investigations have linked them to an alleged drug syndicate that operated in South Africa and Neighbouring countries. The syndicate is mainly run from the Mpumalanga region and locals are asked to be on the look out for these men. Anyone with information about Onyekanna and Ezenwa’s whereabouts are urged to contact Investigating Officer, Warrant Officer Jacob Ras on 0824620760. Chukwuemeka Kingsley Ezenwa.Alias: Alex.     Parents frustrated by a lack of space in Middelburg schools Traffic officers to appear in court for corruption #TrafficAlert: Two dead in Kranspoort accidents VIDEO: Two perish after truck jack-knifes • Save our standby number (072 248 3855) and send us a WhatsApp message with the words “Add me” to be added to our broadcast list. • Like us on Facebook, follow us on Twitter and Instagram. • Subscribe to our YouTube channel. • Click on the link to subscribe to our bi-weekly newsletter via email. Contact our news room on our 24 hr standby number 072 248 3855, or send a mail to our editor tobie@mobserver.co.za